  Large Language Model (ChatGPT)
description: >-
  This study evaluates the accuracy and consistency of a commercially available
  large language model (LLM) in extracting and interpreting sensitivity and
  reliability data from complete visual field (VF) test reports for the
  assessment of glaucomatous defects.
